node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Emotional Quotes 🖤 on September 08, 2021. May be an image of text.

Photo by Emotional Quotes 🖤 on September 06, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'PRINCE$$ @champagnecoco I don't want my child to say "my mom was so strong" and list off all the struggles I survived. I want her to say, my mom was so happy. She was so peaceful, we had so much fun and love.'.

Photo by Emotional Quotes 🖤 on September 06, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Pain Depression & Anxiety @ILLUMINUSNUMB DO?? U?? EVER?? GET?? SCARED?? TO?? GET HAPPY?? BECAUSE?? EVERYTIME?? U?? DO?? YOU'LL?? END ??UP?? SO?? SAD??'.

Photo by Emotional Quotes 🖤 on September 05, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'mom @thewildwatsons If a friend hasn't responded to my text but see them active on social media, it's probably because they are overtired overworked and taking a well-deserved break to scroll. You're not entitled to someone's down time. True friends understand that you can't pour from an empty cup'.

Photo by Emotional Quotes 🖤 on September 04, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'A @baaabylicia If your girlfriend takes birth control go tell her thank you, buy her flowers, or just fucking hug her for an extra second bc those things are literally depression pills & y'all don't realize what they go through just so you can nut'.

Photo by Emotional Quotes 🖤 on September 02, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Xay Yarbroux @hoodopulence Speaking of Blues Clues, y'all remember when Salt and Pepper had Paprika? It was a whole event. You had to be here.'.

Photo by Emotional Quotes 🖤 on August 30, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'gaychel @coochieflop … gf and I were stoned out of our minds holding hands last night and we walk by this couple and one of them goes "look how happy they are why can't we be that happy" baby we are focusing on putting one foot in front of the other rn'.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Emotional Quotes 🖤 on August 28, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'michelle. @michkeenah eldest daughters who intervene in parenting in the hopes that their siblings grow up up less traumatised than them :( yall have my heart fr'.
Photo by Emotional Quotes 🖤 on August 27, 2021. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Maahi @Maahi_M So September is next week?? Im still waiting for summer to start'.

Photo by Emotional Quotes 🖤 on August 27, 2021. May be an image of text that says '7h Dude honestly see people on here that I went to school with since elementary, middle school, and high school and we could have barely even spoken to eachother during those times but when see y'all post pictures of your families and accomplishments I'm genuinely happy for yall. Like my mind will go back to a passing by memory of either us in the same class or recess or lunch and be like "look at us now". wish for ALLLLLL the blessings for y'all 22 1 Comment'.

Photo by Emotional Quotes 🖤 in Saint Johnsbury, Vermont. May be an image of text that says 'Emelyne Museaux @plsleaveamsg "Nobody wants to work anymore." Nobody ever wanted to work at all. We wanted to be productive be creative, be part of a community, be supported, be validated, and have the time and space to truly rest. No one actually wants to trade in hours of their life to "earn" necessities. 5:15 PM 5/12/21 Twitter for iPhone'.
Photo by Emotional Quotes 🖤 on August 25, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'DR1 @luhkeza I can't believe I used to think I was stressed in high school'.
